## Setup

```bash
uv sync                       # install dbt-core + adapter
uv tool install pre-commit    # if not already installed
pre-commit install            # enable git hooks
uv run dbt deps               # install dbt packages
uv run dbt parse              # validate the project (no warehouse needed)
```

Configure your warehouse connection in `profiles.yml` (kept out of git). Then:

```bash
uv run dbt build              # run + test models
```

